    <body>
        <section name="DataNucleus Plugin">
            <p>
                <i>DataNucleus Maven1 Plugin</i> provides a plugin for use of DataNucleus with Maven 1.x.
                <b>This is only supported up to and including AccessPlatform 1.1</b>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Compile Requirement : JDK1.3+</li>
                <li>Runtime Requirement : JDK1.3+</li>
                <li>Latest version : 1.1.0</li>
                <li>Roadmap : <a href="http://issues.datanucleus.org/browse/NUCMAVEN?report=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.project:roadmap-panel" target="_blank">Via JIRA</a></li>
                <li>License : <a href="../project/license.html">Apache 2</a></li>
                <li>Source : <a href="http://datanucleus.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/datanucleus/tools/maven1/trunk/">latest</a></li>
            </ul>

            <subsection name="Download">
                <p><i>DataNucleus Maven1 Plugin</i> is downloadable as following</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><b>Releases</b> <a href="http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=222750&amp;package_id=273217" target="_blank">from SourceForge</a></li>
                    <li><b>Releases</b> <a href="http://www.datanucleus.org/downloads/maven/maven/plugins/" target="_blank">from Maven1 Repository</a></li>
                    <li><b>Nightly builds</b> <a href="http://www.datanucleus.org/downloads/maven-nightly/maven/plugins/" target="_blank">from Maven1 Nightly Repository</a></li>
                </ul>
                <br/>
            </subsection>

            <subsection name="Dependencies">
                <p>
                    <i>DataNucleus Maven1 Plugin</i> is dependent on the following packages of software. 
                    Click on the name to go to the home page for that software to download it.
                </p>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Package</th>
                        <th>Version</th>
                        <th>Description</th>
                        <th width="150">Required?</th>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="core.html">datanucleus-core</a></td>
                        <td>1.0.x</td>
                        <td>Provides logging, localisation, and other framework facilities for DataNucleus</td>
                        <td>Yes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="enhancer.html">datanucleus-enhancer</a></td>
                        <td>1.0.x</td>
                        <td>Bytecode enhancement of classes to be persisted</td>
                        <td>Yes if using enhancement functionality</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="store.rdbms.html">datanucleus-rdbms</a></td>
                        <td>1.0.x</td>
                        <td>Persistence to RDBMS datastore</td>
                        <td>Yes if using SchemaTool functionality</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
                <br/>
                <br/>
            </subsection>
        </section>

